# takefrom-printer regression (synthetic, v2 format). The worker prints until
# holding a value >= 50, feeding rejects to the shredder. Exercises: takefrom on
# a printer (fresh random cube), giveto shredder, randomized trials, and the
# all_holding_min win check.
name Printer Take
dim 3 3
ent printer 1 2
ent shredder 0 1
ent worker 1 1
goal all_holding_min 50
